<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/>
<title>Page Not Found · Lolo Travels™</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@200;300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body{
  background:#060E1A;color:#F5F0E8;
  font-family:'Jost',sans-serif;
  min-height:100vh;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  overflow:hidden;
}
.wrap{text-align:center;padding:40px;position:relative;z-index:2;}
.num{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;
  font-weight:300;
  font-size:clamp(8rem,20vw,18rem);
  color:rgba(201,168,76,.07);
  line-height:1;
  letter-spacing:-.02em;
  position:absolute;
  top:50%;left:50%;
  transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
  pointer-events:none;
  z-index:0;
  white-space:nowrap;
}
.tag{
  font-family:'Jost',sans-serif;font-weight:200;
  font-size:.6rem;letter-spacing:.45em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:rgba(201,168,76,.45);
  margin-bottom:20px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:12px;
}
.tag::before,.tag::after{
  content:'';display:block;width:24px;height:1px;
  background:rgba(201,168,76,.25);
}
h1{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;
  font-weight:300;font-style:italic;
  font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,4.5rem);
  color:#F5F0E8;line-height:1.05;margin-bottom:16px;
}
p{
  font-family:'Jost',sans-serif;font-weight:200;
  font-size:.9rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.42);
  line-height:2;margin-bottom:44px;
  max-width:400px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;
}
.btn{
  display:inline-block;
  font-family:'Jost',sans-serif;font-weight:400;
  font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;
  background:rgba(201,168,76,.9);color:#060E1A;
  padding:16px 52px;
  text-decoration:none;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  transition:letter-spacing .35s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);
}
.btn::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;
  background:#E2C97E;
  transform:translateX(-101%);
  transition:transform .5s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);
}
.btn:hover{letter-spacing:.32em;}
.btn:hover::before{transform:translateX(0);}
.btn span{position:relative;z-index:1;}
.ghost{
  display:inline-block;margin-left:16px;
  font-family:'Jost',sans-serif;font-weight:200;
  font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:rgba(201,168,76,.55);
  text-decoration:none;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.2);
  padding-bottom:2px;
  transition:color .3s,border-color .3s;
}
.ghost:hover{color:rgba(201,168,76,.85);border-color:rgba(201,168,76,.5);}
/* Animated dots */
.dots{
  position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;overflow:hidden;pointer-events:none;
}
.dot{
  position:absolute;
  width:1px;height:1px;
  background:rgba(201,168,76,.4);
  border-radius:50%;
  animation:float linear infinite;
}
@keyframes float{
  0%{transform:translateY(100vh) translateX(0);opacity:0;}
  10%{opacity:.8;}
  90%{opacity:.3;}
  100%{transform:translateY(-80px) translateX(var(--dx,20px));opacity:0;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="dots" id="dots"></div>
<div class="num">404</div>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="tag">Lolo Travels™</div>
  <h1>This page took<br>a detour.</h1>
  <p>The page you are looking for may have moved or no longer exists. Let us get you back on track.</p>
  <div>
    <a href="/" class="btn"><span>Return Home</span></a>
    <a href="/inquiry" class="ghost">Plan a Trip</a>
  </div>
</div>
<script>
var dots = document.getElementById('dots');
for(var i=0;i<28;i++){
  var d = document.createElement('div');
  d.className='dot';
  d.style.left = Math.random()*100+'%';
  d.style.width = d.style.height = (Math.random()*2+1)+'px';
  d.style.setProperty('--dx',(Math.random()*60-30)+'px');
  d.style.animationDuration = (Math.random()*12+8)+'s';
  d.style.animationDelay = (Math.random()*10)+'s';
  dots.appendChild(d);
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
